I have genreated a new bearing faults dataset. The dataset comprises one normal condition and 4 bearing faults dataset (Fault-A,Fault-B,Fault-C and Fault-D). the dataset consist of 5 .lvm files for each fault. the below is the details of dataset columns . 
Column 0--> Current Phase A
Column 1--> Current Phase B
Column 2--> Current Phase C
Befor Gear Box
Column 3--> Accelerometer1 X-axis
Column 4--> Accelerometer1 Y-axis
Column 5--> Accelerometer1 Z-axis
After Gear Box
Column 6--> Accelerometer2 X-axis
Column 7--> Accelerometer2 Y-axis
Column 8--> Accelerometer2 Z-axis
Befor Gear Box
Column 9--> Sound Sensor1
Aftr Gear Box
Column 10--> Sound Sensor2
Column 11--> Water Level Sensor1 digital input
Column 12--> Water Level Sensor2 digital input
Column 13--> Tachometer1 digital input
Column 14--> Tachometer2 digital input
Column 15--> Relay1 digital output
Column 16--> Relay2 digital output


Column0 to Column 10 --> Analog Signals
Column11 to Column 16 --> Digital Signals

Sampling Rate:1600 Hz, Simulation
################ Total number of samples = (57299,17) 
1. Sensor_Data_acquistion_No_Condition (Normal Condition): Total no of samples: 15158
2. Sensor_Data_acquistion - load_2kg (Fault-A): total no of samples: 10574
3. Sensor_Data_acquistion - load_5kg (Fault-B): total no of samples: 10514
4. Sensor_Data_acquistion - load_7kg (Fault-C): total no of samples: 10526
5. Sensor_Data_acquistion - load_10kg (Fault-D): total no of samples: 10527 
